            . I am a pawnbroker; I have all the articles which were pawned by the prisoner at different times.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He did not leave me in care of his house; he left me no keys; his young man had them; I had only the care of the kitchen - I pawned some of the things through distress, and so did my husband; and since I have been in prisoner my husband is dead.</p>
